<!-- Game Cheats Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Play as Female (Marionette) Shadow -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Highlight "Rikuo" on the Character Select screen, hold Select and press any button.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Play as Darkstalkers Rikuo -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>At the character select screen highlight the ? box and press Select 7 times, then press any button</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Play as Image Talbain -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Highlight Talbain and hold Select, then press all three Punch buttons at once</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Play as Lilligan-
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Highlight "Lillith" on the Character Select screen, hold select and press any button.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Play as Male Shadow -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>At the character select screen highlight the ? box and press Select 5 times. Then press any button.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Play as Memory Restored Victor -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Highlight "Victor" on the Character Select screen, hold Select and press any button.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Play as Night Warriors Talbain-
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>At the character select screen, highlight Talbain, hold the Select button and press all three Punch buttons together.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Play as Shin Bishamon(Oboro)-
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Highlight Bishamon at the character selection screen. Then, hold Select and press any two Punch or Kick buttons simultaneously. Alternatively, highlight Bishamon, then hold L2 then press any Punch or Kick.</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
	</table>
       	</td>

     </tr>
</table>

